	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was trying to quickly slap together a second game, for the competition. (Half done)<br /><br />But, it's based entirely on another game, that I now see is covered by a Creative Commons License...<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/3.0/">https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/3.0/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />So, I don't think it could legally go on a for-profit multicart. I may have to release it as a free to download only.<br /><br />Thoughts?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
