	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Quick question - Licensing Issue</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Most &quot;clone&quot; video games are considered legal, as long as they don't take the actual art/text/music/etc. from the original. Game design is usually very difficult to copyright. Whether or not they're ethical is another story.<br /><br />You could just ask the original author about it; just because they licensed it as CC doesn't mean they can't also license it to you in a different way, should they want to.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


